_sText:
Something I made when I was bored. I figure someone could do something with it, maybe a knife arena or something. Be aware that it uses quite a lot of brushes.

The version in the download has a 3D skybox too, which isn't shown in the screenshots. You may want to delete that.

The skybox should be remade to fit if you are going to use this. I simply made it a box as I was only quickly testing it.

Water texture is included. Simply drop the materials folder into your cstrike folder. The material is named "water_flat".
